mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes the articles entitled "From the Floor", "Square Dance Date Book", "On the Record and Record Report", "As I See It", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "Discovery - Department for New Square Dancers", "Style Series: Everybody Chain", "Ladies on the Square", "Round the Outside Ring", "The Workshop", "Paging the Roundancers: Jerry and Phyllis Wareham", "Experimental Lab", and "The Caller of the Month: Jack Murtha".
